# Interior Design ERP - Pencil.dev Design Specs

## 1. Global Themes
- **Background**: #F9F9F7 (Cream White)
- **Primary Text**: #1A1A1A (Deep Charcoal)
- **Accent 1**: #C29D9D (Muted Rose)
- **Accent 2**: #9CA89C (Sage Green)
- **Font**: Cormorant Garamond (Serif), Inter (Sans)

## 2. Page: AI Estimation Workspace
- **[Canvas Area]**: Central floor plan image with SVG overlays.
- **[Component: DetectionBox]**: 
  - Border: 2px solid var(--accent-rose)
  - Fill: rgba(194, 157, 157, 0.1)
  - Label: Floating pill on top-left.
- **[Component: EstimateTable]**: 
  - Grouped by "Sections" (Living Room, Infrastructure).
  - Hover state on rows to show "AI Fix" button.

## 4. Page: Client Management (CRM)
- **[List View]**: Minimalist grid with client cards. 
- **[Client Profile]**: 
  - Left side: Basic info & Timeline of contact logs (Interactive feed).
  - Right side: Visual mood board (preferred styles) & linked projects.
- **[Interaction]**: One-click "Start Project" from client profile.

## 5. Page: Vendor & WorkCrew Directory (SCM)
- **[Category Filters]**: Chips for "Material", "Equipment", "Carpentry", "Plumbing".
- **[Vendor Card]**: 
  - Header: Verified badge & Rating (Star system).
  - Body: Core specialties, primary contact, bank info snippet.
- **[Inventory Insight]**: Linked PDF catalogs preview (using a masonry layout).

## 6. Page: AI Lab (Image-to-Image)
- **[Generation Workspace]**:
  - Image Uploader for "Base Draft".
  - Style Selection Drawer: (Nordic, Industrial, Japandi, etc.).
  - Prompt Refinement Input: Natural language adjustments.
  - Result Strip: Showing historical generations for comparison.

## 7. Page: Workflow Configurator (Settings)
- **[Canvas Area]**: Node-based visual editor.
- **[Step Node]**: 
  - Fields: Title (e.g., Manager Approval), Approver Type (Role/Individual), Threshold (Amount > $X).
  - Relationship Lines: Visual arrows showing the flow.
- **[Template Library]**: Pre-saved flows for "Small Project" vs "Premium Project".

## 8. Page: Financial Analytics
- **[Project P&L]**: Progress bar of budget vs actual spend.
- **[Matrix]**: Incoming payments (Receivables) vs Outgoing vendor payments (Payables).
- **[Chart]**: Monthly revenue/profit line chart in Accent Rose.

## 9. Component: Project Workspace Tabs
- **[Quotation Tool]**: The existing dual-pane AI workspace.
- **[Contract Management]**: 
  - View signed contract PDF.
  - Milestone tracking (Deposit, 2nd Stage, Final).
- **[Financials (P&L)]**: 
  - Real-time margin calculation (Total Quotation - Total Vendor Expenses).
  - Visual gauge for "Profit Health".
